{
  "stem": "8610.2",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "But to give an idea-- example of an idea, of how the military people didn't appreciate this situation, I was called in by the major in charge of the camp, who said to me, you know, these people are behaving very badly.",
      "word_count": 42
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] He found a woman had cut up an army blanket and made a dress of it-- out of it.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "But what she didn't know-- that the letters 'WD' stand for 'War Department.' And this was right in the back of the dress, the letters WD.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And this major said, they are abusing army property, misusing army property.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "I said to him, come off it.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "Come off it.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "You know, she's actually made herself a dress.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "She-- she's been living in these horrible pajamas that the Nazis had dressed them in.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "Now she wants to behave like a human being.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "Well, they mustn't use Army property.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "Well, we laughed it off.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "But this was the sort of attitude.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] [SIGHS] But something else was happening in the camp, which I find-- I still, as I think of it, is quite remarkable.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "The power of survival is quite amazing.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] They-- in Belsen, they established a Central Jewish Committee.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "One dynamic little man by the name of Yossele Rosensaft was the moving, moving figure in this.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "He was indestructible.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "He'd been pushed from one camp to another and survived.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "He stood about 5 foot 2 in his socks, but energy beyond recognition.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "And he organized this committee.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "And they had several departments-- one on hygiene, one on culture, one on the secretariat recording, so that they should record the names of survivors and so on, a highly organized government within a government, as it were, inside the camp.",
      "word_count": 41
    }
  ],
